    {
      "idRef": {
        "id": "9c32e1fd27d33ebac4985b93"
      },
      "index": 4,
      "text": "Good. I also advise discretion in this matter since IE isn't sure even if Professor Bambo is still alive or even if regular communications are safe. You could well be walking into a trap, so exercise extreme caution. \n\nGoodbye and good luck.",
      "branches": [
        {
