    {
      "idRef": {
        "id": "9c2644e1ff0676440b23f43f"
      },
      "index": 6,
      "text": "Well, someone already seems to be on a [[DM.BaseDescriptionDefs[LoreLosTech],LosTech]] fool's errand, the question is if we'll be the next ones drawn into this black hole, besides this Professor Bambo. \n\nMaybe Lord Karosas had the right idea in walking out of this.",
      "branches": [
        {
