      "speaker_override_id": "598cd3f26230355c18000069",
      "actions": null,
      "comment": ""
    },
    {
      "idRef": {
        "id": "9c0370d180ca64e728efc7c3"
      },
      "index": 8,
      "text": "Yeah, I've noticed their propaganda calling the Periphery to a return of the [[DM.BaseDescriptionDefs[LoreRimWorldsRepublic],Rim Worlds Republic]] era and away from Inner Sphere corruption.\n\n They have quite an influence in the Taurian Concordat's government, and are heavily armed.",
      "branches": [
        {
          "responseText": "",
          "conditions": null,
          "actions": null,
          "nextNodeIndex": 9,
          "hideIfUnavailable": true,
          "onlyOnce": false,
