      "comment": ""
    },
    {
      "idRef": {
        "id": "9cd062466c638f84b6061f41"
      },
      "index": 10,
      "text": "Look, 'Professor' Bambo is known to be a discredited pseudoscience fraud, who sells conspiracy theories about unknown artifacts being recovered across the Periphery, technologies like [[DM.BaseDescriptionDefs[LoreHPG],HPG]] gates for instantaneous 'Mech travel across stars, or that the whole universe is nothing more than a computer [[DM.BaseDescriptionDefs[LoreBattleTech],simulation]] run by interdimensional beings.",
      "branches": [
        {
          "responseText": "",
          "conditions": null,
          "actions": null,
          "nextNodeIndex": 11,
          "hideIfUnavailable": true,
          "onlyOnce": false,
          "idRef": {
            "id": "9cca42a349c7db12033bb3d2"
          },
          "inputBypass": false,
          "auxiliaryLink": false,
          "comment": ""
        }
      ],
      "nodeType": 1,
      "truthValue": false,
      "autoFollowBranchDelay": 1,
      "inputMaxLength": 0,
      "sourceTopicRef": null,
      "subjectTopicRefs": [],
      "sourceInSceneRef": null,
      "sourceWithTagInScene": "",
      "override_speaker": null,
      "speaker_override_id": "59b98a97623035ac140056c6",
      "actions": null,
      "comment": ""
    },
    {
      "idRef": {
        "id": "9c85c2a613bd26fc0b1be742"
      },
      "index": 11,
      "text": "Academically, he never actually presented any concrete proof of his claims and he is widely known to sell any [[DM.BaseDescriptionDefs[LoreLosTech],LosTech]] recovered from his expeditions to the highest bidder.\n\nIn reality we're dealing with a treasure hunter and a publicity artist, which basically says a lot about IE. ",
      "branches": [
        {
          "responseText": "",
          "conditions": null,
          "actions": null,
          "nextNodeIndex": 12,
          "hideIfUnavailable": true,
          "onlyOnce": false,
