    {
      "idRef": {
        "id": "9cb5a34b5669772135117a8d"
      },
      "index": 12,
      "text": "It seems that he cares about the [[DM.BaseDescriptionDefs[LoreCBill],C-Bills]] first, so we have that in common. \n\nIt should at least be valuable LosTech, despite whomever the owner is. I guess that covers all significant factors to consider here, as far as I'm concerned.",
      "branches": [
