    {
      "idRef": {
        "id": "9cec3a9e34bcf9403051d54f"
      },
      "index": 13,
      "text": "Not so fast, Yang. \n\nIf the Professor decided to steal something from the Creed, then I'm worried about what they might have found, since these guys' ancestors threw nukes at SLDF garrisons during the [[DM.BaseDescriptionDefs[LoreReunificationWar],Reunification War]].",
      "branches": [
        {
          "responseText": "",
          "conditions": null,
          "actions": null,
          "nextNodeIndex": 14,
          "hideIfUnavailable": true,
          "onlyOnce": false,
