    {
      "idRef": {
        "id": "9ceab964e651f44850b873e0"
      },
      "index": 14,
      "text": "Yeah, we can also encounter aliens, if you believe the tabloid holovids Darius. \n\nProfessor Murad already said that the guy is a con artist, and it doesn't sound as if he was trying to steal a derelict [[DM.BaseDescriptionDefs[LoreWarShip],WarShip]]. So whatever his expedition found, it can't be that big, most likely just an old SLDF dump that happened to be recovered by the Creed first.",
      "branches": [
        {
          "responseText": "",
          "conditions": null,
          "actions": null,
          "nextNodeIndex": 15,
          "hideIfUnavailable": true,
          "onlyOnce": false,
