    {
      "idRef": {
        "id": "9cab69025a528567fcd1d752"
      },
      "index": 15,
      "text": "Honestly, I couldn't care less if Professor Bambo was left to rot in a stinky Periphery prison. But as Yang said, he's usually interested in items that can be carried and sold easily, so we shouldn't have any surprises in what he recovered, or stole from the Creed. ",
